---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About — Last Page" active="about">
  <div class="static-wrap">
    <h1 class="static-title">About</h1>
    <div class="static-body">
      <p>
        I am amal.v — online, O IV, after Ozymandias. This is Last Page,
        a personal site where I write essays, blogs, verse, and notes on
        cinema, memory, politics, ideology, sport, and the quiet tensions
        of an ordinary life.
      </p>
      <p>
        There is no algorithm here, no audience to perform for. Just thinking
        out loud, in public, for the record.
      </p>
      <p>
        I live in Pune. I read a lot. If something here resonates,
        leave a comment or find me on X or Reddit.
      </p>
      <h2>Why the name?</h2>
      <p>
        O IV — Ozymandiasiv. The Shelley poem. A king who built monuments
        to his own greatness. The desert remains. The monuments don't.
        Everything you write is the last page of something.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
